title: That moment when...
content:
You realize you haven't posted on your blog 13 days and let go of your record GitHub streak. Wow. I really need to get with the blogging program. So nobody knows what I've done in the last 13 days. Here's a list:

  • I don't have to wear my retainer during the day anymore
  • I wrote a BBCode parser in python
  • I wrote a web server with socket in python
  • I tried to create low poly with scratch (and failed)
  • I discovered that non-semitone notes do not translate to non-decimal hertz values
  • I aced 2 tests at school
That's pretty much it (unless I count other stuff I made :P)
